snippet.title: Abrakadaboom is coming to early access!
snippet.description:
Get ready to become a wizard and lose some hard-earned friendships, Abrakadaboom is coming to early access on April 18th, 2019 on PC via Steam for $19.99 (UK: £15.40 - EU: 17,90 €).

Store : https://store.steampowered.com/app/979000/Abrakadaboom/
Website : https://www.abrakadaboom-game.com

Also Check :
Facebook : https://www.facebook.com/Abrakadaboom-355440485023430
Twitter : https://twitter.com/AbrakadaboomG

--- 🇫🇷 ---
Préparez-vous à devenir magicien et à perdre quelques amitiés durement acquises, car Abrakadaboom arrive en accès anticipé le 18 avril 2018 sur PC via Steam pour 17,90 € (US: $19.99 - UK: £15.40).
-----------

Music : 
“Ask Rufus”, music by audionautix.com
“Happy Rock”, music by bensound.com (http://www.bensound.com/royalty-free-music)
